<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="..\config8\suzuki.xsl" ?><!DOCTYPE suzuki [<!ENTITY % sdatacharaents SYSTEM "..\config8\sdatacharaents.txt">%sdatacharaents;]><suzuki><manual>
<section sectnbr = "4A">
<servcat sctnbr = "04" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AGEAP70A4106021" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Bremskraftverstärker-Funktionsprüfung
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Vor dieser Überprüfung unbedingt sicherstellen, dass sich keine Luft in den Hydraulikleitungen befindet.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servinfosub id = "AGEAP70A4106021001">
<title>
Luftdichtigkeit überprüfen
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Den Motor anlassen.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Nach 1 bis 2 Minuten Betrieb den Motor ausschalten.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Das Bremspedal mehrmals mit der gleichen Kraft wie bei einer Normalbremsung drücken und dabei auf Änderungen des Pedalwegs achten. Der Bremskraftverstärker ist dicht, wenn sich der Pedalweg bei jeder Pedalbetätigung verringert.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.619mm" ver = "01" gw = "131" gh = "126"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "6" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.501in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.579in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "0.631in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
1. Gang
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
2. Gang
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
3. Gang
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Falls sich der Pedalweg nicht ändert, ist der Bremskraftverstärker undicht.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Bei mangelhafter Funktion die Unterdruckleitungen sowie Dichtungen überprüfen und defekte Teile austauschen. Danach den gesamten Test wiederholen.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.196mm" ver = "01" gw = "132" gh = "125"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.030in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
1., 2., 3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AGEAP70A4106021002">
<title>
Funktionsprüfung
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Bei ausgeschaltetem Motor das Bremspedal mehrmals mit der gleichen Kraft drücken und sicherstellen, dass sich der Pedalweg nicht ändert.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410007.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.323mm" ver = "01" gw = "162" gh = "126"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Den Motor anlassen und gleichzeitig das Bremspedal durchtreten. Verlängert sich der Pedalweg geringfügig, so ist die Funktion des Bremskraftverstärkers zufriedenstellend. Keinerlei Änderung des Pedalwegs weist auf einen Defekt des Bremskraftverstärkers hin.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410008.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.958mm" ver = "01" gw = "173" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AGEAP70A4106021003">
<title>
Luftdichtigkeit unter Last prüfen
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Bei laufendem Motor das Bremspedal durchtreten. Den Motor ausschalten, während das Bremspedal weiterhin betätigt bleibt.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410009.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.805mm" ver = "01" gw = "123" gh = "130"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.232in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.628in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
H: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Halten
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Das Bremspedal 30 Sekunden lang durchgetreten halten. Bleibt die Pedalhöhe unverändert, ist der Bremskraftverstärker einwandfrei. Falls sich die Pedalhöhe ändert, ist der Bremskraftverstärker mangelhaft.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410010.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.059mm" ver = "01" gw = "192" gh = "131"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.382in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.643in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.382in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.800in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
H: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Halten
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
T: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
30 Sekunden
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
